### 1. Получить JWT токен (логин)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Статистика дашборда (требует токен)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Мои задачи — все
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Мои задачи — только "В работе"
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/tasks?status=InProgress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Команда
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/team
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Активность команды
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Календарь (май 2024)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/dashboard/calendar?year=2024&month=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
